    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Select the <em>TrackBar </em>orientation with the 'TrackBar orientation' ComboBox and orientation of the demonstrated <em>TrackBar </em>will be change, respectively.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The <em>TrackBar </em>contains <em>Orientation </em>property that indicates the <em>Horizontal </em>or <em>Vertical </em>orientation of the track bar.</p>]]></Paragraph>
